border.disabled=var(--color-border-disabled)
radius=var(--radius-md)[8px]
borderWidth=var(--border-width-default)[1px]

## Do & Don't
✅ **Do**
- Utiliser les CSS custom properties (var(--component-*))
- Respecter les états interactifs (hover, active, focus, disabled)
- Vérifier la fidélité visuelle avec la maquette Figma

❌ **Don't**
- Ne pas utiliser de valeurs brutes (px, #hex) — utiliser les tokens
- Ne pas supprimer les états d'accessibilité (:focus-visible)
- Ne pas modifier les dimensions sans vérifier la spec Figma

## 💻 Code interactif (Live Editor)

```jsx
const __css = `.input-wrapper {
  display: inline-flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--spacing-xs, 4px);
  width: 100%;
}
.input {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--spacing-sm, 8px);
  width: 100%;
  font-family: var(--font-family-default, Inter);
  font-weight: 400;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md, 8px);
  border: var(--border-width-default, 1px) solid var(--color-border-default, #D1D5DB);
  background: var(--color-bg-primary, #FFFFFF);
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  transition: border-color 150ms ease-in-out, box-shadow 150ms ease-in-out;
  outline: none;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.input::placeholder { color: var(--color-text-tertiary, #9CA3AF); }
.input:hover:not(:disabled):not(.input--error) { border-color: var(--color-border-strong, #9CA3AF); }
.input:focus-visible, .input--focus {
  border-color: var(--color-border-focus, #3B82F6);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--color-border-focus, #3B82F6);
}
.input--error { border-color: var(--color-danger-500, #DC2626); }
.input--error:focus-visible { box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--color-danger-500, #DC2626); }
.input:disabled, .input--disabled {
  background: var(--color-bg-disabled, #F9FAFB);
  color: var(--color-text-disabled, #D1D5DB);
  border-color: var(--color-border-disabled, #E5E7EB);
  cursor: not-allowed;
}
/* Sizes */
.input--sm {
  min-height: 32px;
  padding: var(--spacing-xs, 4px) var(--spacing-sm, 8px);
  font-size: var(--font-size-sm, 14px);
  line-height: 20px;
}
.input--md {
  min-height: 40px;
  padding: var(--spacing-sm, 8px);
  font-size: var(--font-size-md, 16px);
  line-height: 24px;
}
.input--lg {
  min-height: 48px;
  padding: var(--spacing-sm, 8px) var(--spacing-md, 16px);
  font-size: var(--font-size-lg, 18px);
  line-height: 28px;
}
.input-label {
  font-size: var(--font-size-sm, 14px);
  font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium, 500);
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
}
.input-error-msg {
  font-size: var(--font-size-sm, 14px);
  color: var(--color-danger-500, #DC2626);
}`;

const Input = ({
  size = 'md',
  state,
  label,
  id,
  errorMessage,
  placeholder = 'Placeholder...',
  disabled,
  ...props
}) => {
  const isError = state === 'error';
  const isDisabled = disabled || state === 'disabled';
  const inputId = id || `input-${size}`;
  return (
    <div className="input-wrapper">
      {label && <label className="input-label" htmlFor={inputId}>{label}</label>}
      <input
        id={inputId}
        className={`input input--${size}${isError ? ' input--error' : ''}${isDisabled ? ' input--disabled' : ''}`}
        placeholder={placeholder}
        disabled={isDisabled}
        aria-invalid={isError}
        aria-describedby={isError && errorMessage ? `${inputId}-error` : undefined}
        {...props}
      />
      {isError && errorMessage && (
        <span id={`${inputId}-error`} className="input-error-msg" role="alert">{errorMessage}</span>
      )}
    </div>
  );
};

// Demo
const App = () => (
  <div style={{display:'flex',flexDirection:'column',gap:16,padding:16,maxWidth:360}}>
    <Input size="sm" label="Small" placeholder="Small input" />
    <Input size="md" label="Medium" placeholder="Medium input" />
    <Input size="lg" label="Large" placeholder="Large input" />
    <Input size="md" label="Focus" state="focus" placeholder="Focused" />
    <Input size="md" label="Error" state="error" errorMessage="Champ requis" placeholder="Error state" />
    <Input size="md" label="Disabled" state="disabled" placeholder="Disabled" />
  </div>
);

render(<><style>{__css}</style><Input /></>);
```

## ⚠️ Tokens manquants (à créer dans Figma)
var(--color-border-strong) | hover border | #9CA3AF
var(--color-border-disabled) | disabled border | #E5E7EB
var(--color-text-tertiary) | placeholder color | #9CA3AF
var(--font-size-lg) | fontSize lg | 18px

